{"id":584401,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【图说天朝】喷漆示众：广东鳌江镇10户房屋被喷/","date":"2018-05-10T08:59:29Z","modified":"2018-05-10T08:59:29Z","title":"【图说天朝】喷漆示众：广东鳌江镇10户房屋被喷“涉毒家庭”","content":"<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510073403847.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-584405\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510073403847.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"184\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510073403847.png 623w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510073403847-300x123.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584406\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510074844723.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-584406\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510074844723.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"206\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510074844723.png 541w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/20180510074844723-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">“平安鳌江”曾在官微上宣传此事，现已删除原文；网络图片</span></p></div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2118084\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">澎湃新闻 | 广东鳌江镇禁毒办回应十家房屋被喷漆字“涉毒家庭”：正去除</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>5月9日，澎湃新闻从惠来县公安局、惠来县委宣传部证实，该县鳌江镇确实有家庭房屋被喷漆“涉毒家庭”。</p>\n<p>惠来县公安局一名工作人员告诉澎湃新闻，她知道此事，但上述喷漆行为并不县公安局组织的。惠来县政府办公室工作人员称，上述喷漆行为是鳌江镇政府组织的。</p>\n<p>惠来县委办公室一林姓工作人员向澎湃新闻表示，被喷漆的十个家庭来自五个村，均涉及较大制贩毒案件的家庭，喷漆“涉毒家庭”的行为有得到当地村民的同意。目前，“涉毒家庭”的字样还没有涂掉。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584410\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/j7_X-haichqz3662816.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584402\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/j7_X-haichqz3662816.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/j7_X-haichqz3662816.jpg 797w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/j7_X-haichqz3662816-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/j7_X-haichqz3662816-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/VgET-haichqz3662825.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584403\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/VgET-haichqz3662825.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/VgET-haichqz3662825.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/VgET-haichqz3662825-300x159.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/VgET-haichqz3662825-768x406.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ZLgm-fzrwiaz5169974.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584404\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ZLgm-fzrwiaz5169974.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"268\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ZLgm-fzrwiaz5169974.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ZLgm-fzrwiaz5169974-300x161.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ZLgm-fzrwiaz5169974-768x412.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下